      <span>
        <strong>Need help?</strong> See our <a href="/help" style="color:#1070c5;text-decoration:underline;">FAQ</a> or <a href="mailto:support@fcahpt.edu.ng" style="color:#1070c5;text-decoration:underline;">contact support</a>.
